OL,3,CChild in critical condition after
OL,4,Cbeing involved in crash with police
OL,5,Cvehicle
OL,7,FTwo children were taken to hospital
OL,8,Ffollowing a serious collision
OL,9,Finvolving a police car in Cumbria.
OL,11,FThe collision was reported at 5:58pm
OL,12,Fon Saturday 18 April in Senhouse
OL,13,FStreet, Maryport and involved two
OL,14,Fpedestrians, both children of
OL,15,Fsecondary school age.
OL,17,FOne of the children remains in a
OL,18,Fcritical but stable condition while
OL,19,Fthe other, who suffered minor
OL,20,Finjuries, has been discharged from
OL,21,Fhospital.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
