PN,35302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776708666
OL,3,CChild in critical condition after
OL,4,Cbeing involved in crash with police
OL,5,Cvehicle
OL,7,FCumbria Police said the vehicle was
OL,8,Fnot in in pursuit or responding to an
OL,9,Femergency incident at the time of the
OL,10,Fcollision.
OL,12,FThe circumstances of the collision are
OL,13,Fbeing fully investigated, and the
OL,14,Fincident was immediately referred to
OL,15,Fthe Independent Office for Police
OL,16,FConduct, which is standard practice.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
