OL,3,CChild in critical condition after
OL,4,Cbeing involved in crash with police
OL,5,Cvehicle
OL,7,FAnyone who witnessed the collision or
OL,8,Fmay have relevant dashcam or camera
OL,9,Ffootage is asked to get in touch by
OL,10,Fvisiting www.cumbria.police.uk/report-
OL,11,Fit, or calling 101, referencing
OL,12,Fincident number 184 of 18 April.
OL,14,FSuperintendent Sarah Jones, Cumbria
OL,15,FConstabulary said: "Our thoughts are
OL,16,Fwith the two young people involved in
OL,17,Fthis incident and their families.
